{"title":"世界上有这样的人","authors":["叶维民"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上有这样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶维民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他不要什么报酬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知道疲倦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人类的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作着，工作着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能忍得住难以忍耐的艰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能挺得住敌人各种引诱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能经得起死的考验"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢而坚定的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人类的幸福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗着，战斗着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他具有人类最大的智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他具有人类最好的品质"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他具有人类最高的理想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他具有人类最深刻的爱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是人类最好的儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他，共产党人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有这样的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他为了创造人类美好的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他牺牲了一切一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是太阳使世界发光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们颂赞吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这人类中的精华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月六日（八月十五）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}